<%- include('partials/head', { title, description, path, SITE_URL }) %>
<%- include('partials/header', { active }) %>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
    <span class="eyebrow">Our Story</span>
    <h1>Two friends, a 3D printer, and a lot of late nights.</h1>
    <p class="lead">Ash &amp; Sha started in a spare bedroom in Fort McMurray, Alberta — and it's still run from our home studio today.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container split">
    <div class="split-visual" data-aos="fade-up">
      <img src="/assets/product-cord-winder.svg" alt="Cord winder set">
    </div>
    <div class="split-copy" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="120">
      <span class="eyebrow">How we started</span>
      <h2>Solving our own annoying problems</h2>
      <p>It started with a wobbly kitchen shelf and a missing cabinet peg. After printing a quick replacement that worked perfectly, we realized: if this was annoying us, it was probably annoying a lot of other people too.</p>
      <p>From there, Ash &amp; Sha grew into a small catalog of clever, practical, and sometimes just plain fun 3D printed goods — each one designed, tested, and refined right here at home before it ever reaches you.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head center" data-aos="fade-up">
      <span class="eyebrow">What we believe</span>
      <h2>Small batch. Big care.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="icon-wrap">🌱</div>
        <h3>Made to order</h3>
        <p>We print after you order — no warehouses full of unsold stock, no unnecessary waste.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="80">
        <div class="icon-wrap">🛠️</div>
        <h3>Designed in-house</h3>
        <p>Every product starts as our own 3D model, prototyped and tested before it goes live.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="160">
        <div class="icon-wrap">🏡</div>
        <h3>Home studio, real people</h3>
        <p>We're a two-person operation based in Fort McMurray — every order is packed by hand.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="240">
        <div class="icon-wrap">🇨🇦</div>
        <h3>Proudly Canadian</h3>
        <p>Designed, printed, and shipped from Alberta — supporting a small Canadian business.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-band" data-aos="fade-up">
      <div class="cta-band-content">
        <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light">Get in touch</span>
        <h2>Got a custom idea? We'd love to hear it.</h2>
        <p>From accessibility aids to custom branded items, if it can be printed, we can probably make it.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer', { year }) %>
